                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Can lnet route a client with 2 hops between client and server.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;client(o2ib1)&#160;&amp;lt;&#8211;&amp;gt; (o2ib1) rtr1 (o2ib2) &amp;lt;&#8211;&amp;gt;&#160;(o2ib2) rtr2 (o2ib3) &amp;lt;&#8211;&amp;gt; (o2ib3) server&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
